    26	## 0. Method, and what the supervisor actually tests
    27	
    28	### 0.1 The quantities the shipped supervisor compares (`crates/pnt-integrity`)
    29	
    30	The proposal is bound to what the built supervisor (unit U-A1, CONTRACTS v5.1) actually
