    46	
    47	### 0.2 Coverage factors (acceptance profile → per-epoch protection limit)
    48	
    49	`SAFETY_CASE.md` §0 requires per-epoch protection limits **no looser than the active
    50	acceptance profile implies**, and the baseline's acceptance numbers are *error* limits
    51	(actual error vs truth, at a percentile whose exact confidence definition is itself
