    53	*reported one-sigma DRMS*. Converting one to the other needs a coverage factor. This proposal
    54	uses a **two-sided margin factor `k = 2`** on horizontal position: a protection limit
    55	expressed as one-sigma DRMS, tested at `≤ PL`, keeps the **2-DRMS** bound (≈ 95–98 % of
